FT  11 NOV 94 / UK Company News: Warner Howard ahead
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Warner Howard, which rents and distributes laundry and catering equipment,
reported a 7.2 per cent advance in pre-tax profits from Pounds 3.22m to
Pounds 3.46m in the six months to August 31.
