Turnover advanced from Pounds 10.7m to Pounds 11.1m, a rise of 4 per cent.
Earnings per share were 9.76p (9.11p). The interim dividend is raised to
2.8p (2.27p) partly to reduce disparity between the interim and final
payments and partly to reflect the company's growing cash generation and
liquidity.
