<HEADLINE>
FT  11 NOV 94 / FT columnist wins
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Lucy Kellaway, Financial Times management columnist, has won the management
award in the 1994 Industrial Journalism Awards, sponsored by Texaco and
organised by the Industrial Society.
</TEXT>
